09:49.860 --> 09:54.500
 Then you have these other classes of compounds

09:54.500 --> 09:56.660
 that you could call psychedelic.

09:56.660 --> 09:59.240
 Another big one would be the NMDA antagonist.

09:59.240 --> 10:03.460
 So this would include ketamine, PCP, and dextromethorphan,

