33:14.040 --> 33:15.680
 So for people that don't necessarily understand

33:15.680 --> 33:17.640
 the relationship between what we call ligand,

33:17.640 --> 33:19.400
 the thing that parks in the receptor,

33:19.400 --> 33:21.240
